(42482, 58464, 3858, 1, 'FASHION INTRO', '', '2011-12-31 00:00:00', 2000, 20, 0, 7, 'Kiss kiss(lil mom she wants my) \r\nHug hug (and I shall give you all my) \r\nkiss kiss(you''ve been asking for more)\r\nHug hug(only you I never say no)\r\nKiss kiss hug hug (from the mid night to the sun rise)\r\nkiss kiss hug hug (from Taipei to California)\r\nkiss kiss hug hug (you will love my)\r\nkiss kiss hug hug (feeling damn right)\r\nI’m not a model.\r\nOnly know how to walk.\r\nOnly know how to pose.\r\nOnly know how to walk, walk, stalk.\r\n\r\nCause I’ve got thought.\r\nCause I am fashion.\r\nCause I’ve got style. \r\nOh yeah~Kiss kiss hug hug (kiss kiss hug hug) \r\nYEAH! YEAH! OH YEAH! \r\nYEAH! YEAH! OH YEAH!\r\n\r\nSometimes they’re in my head.\r\nLike they are whispering.\r\nOther time they’re deep in my heart, my vein, my head, my everywhere.\r\nSay X. (X.) Say O. (O.) Say X.O.X.O. (X.O.X.O.)\r\nYou guys must follow.\r\nCheck out the way we dance.\r\nCheck out the way we play the music.\r\nCheck out the way we play the song, song, thong.\r\n\r\nCause we’ve got thought.\r\nCause we are fashion.\r\nCause we’ve got style. \r\nOh yeah~Kiss kiss hug hug (kiss kiss hug hug)\r\nYEAH! OH YEAH! \r\nYEAH! OH YEAH!\r\n', '', 198, '', '', '', '', '', '', 1, 1, 0, '2012-01-20 19:04:22', '2015-03-12 13:50:06', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
